and he's asleep in the other room

00:00:04.002 --> 00:00:06.021
but I wanna answer you

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.120
my relationship with my children changed after leaving my marriage

00:00:10.121 --> 00:00:12.221
because I no longer had

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:13.500
like you say

