so you know we have the big blow up argument

00:00:23.962 --> 00:00:26.441
and then it's gonna take days to sort that out

00:00:26.442 --> 00:00:27.441
the feelings and everything

00:00:27.442 --> 00:00:28.661
and in those days

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:30.720
I'm not really gonna be present with my children

00:00:30.721 --> 00:00:33.341
because I'm so distracted at the hurt and pain

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:36.400
and confusion of what's going on in my relationship

