so you know I'm spending my days kind of pushing my kids away like hey

00:00:40.282 --> 00:00:40.881
yeah yeah yeah

00:00:40.882 --> 00:00:41.921
can you go do something else

00:00:41.922 --> 00:00:42.441
can you do this

00:00:42.442 --> 00:00:43.281
can you do that

00:00:43.282 --> 00:00:44.241
cause I'm trying to like

