I'm tryna hide what's going on from them

00:00:49.442 --> 00:00:49.801
cause you know

00:00:49.802 --> 00:00:50.921
you don't wanna fight in front of the kids

00:00:50.922 --> 00:00:51.961
so there's just like

00:00:51.962 --> 00:00:55.201
the whole relationship with the kids is very superficial

00:00:55.202 --> 00:00:57.281
cause I'm hiding so much from them

00:00:57.282 --> 00:00:58.701
so the minute I left

00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:02.120
I had no choice but to be authentic and vulnerable in front of them

00:01:02.121 --> 00:01:03.761
there was no longer anything to hide behind

00:01:03.762 --> 00:01:05.021
I no longer had this

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:08.160
relationship that I was running behind closed doors to argue about

00:01:08.161 --> 00:01:09.401
I now had to like

00:01:09.402 --> 00:01:11.361
just be there and be present with my kids

00:01:11.362 --> 00:01:13.501
and it fucking paid off

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:17.180
like I know when you're trying to hide arguing from the kids you kind of

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:18.320
you also hide your emotions

00:01:18.321 --> 00:01:19.401
cause you don't wanna be like

00:01:19.402 --> 00:01:21.881
oh I'm crying cause Mommy and daddy got in an argument

00:01:21.882 --> 00:01:23.181
so you're just like

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:27.480
you know constantly hiding and lying everything from your children

00:01:27.481 --> 00:01:30.801
so there's no way you're gonna have that deep of a relationship

